author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Scanfil Oct-Dec ‍Turnover Total EUR 144.4 Million, Up To 18.1 PCT​
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - SCANFIL OYJ :
* OCT-DEC ‍TURNOVER TOTALLED EUR 144.4 MILLION (Q4 2016: 122.3), UP TO 18.1%​
* Q4 PROFIT WAS EUR 10.5 MILLION (1.3) * ‍ESTIMATES, THAT ITS TURNOVER FOR 2018 WILL BE EUR 530 - 570 MILLION AND OPERATING PROFIT WILL AMOUNT TO EUR 33 - 37 MILLION.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
